                          "content": "A \"Super Randonneur\" is a rider who successfully completes a full series of 200, 300, 400, and 600 km brevets within the same calendar year. Earning this title is a major milestone and serves as the mandatory qualification to ride extreme distances like 1000km, 1200km, and the legendary Paris-Brest-Paris.",
