                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "descendants": {
                    "At1fI": {
                      "content": "Q: What is a brevet?"
                    },
                    "lyRkf": {
                      "content": "A: A brevet is a long-distance cycling event within prescribed time limits in a non-competitive nature. It is not a race."
                    }
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "BLnwM",
                  "type": "ref",
                  "ref": "ZbSPm",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#F0F4F8",
                  "descendants": {
                    "At1fI": {
                      "content": "Q: Do I need to bring my own bike?"
                    },
                    "lyRkf": {
                      "content": "A: Yes, you must provide your own bicycle. It must be human-powered and road-worthy. Ebikes are generally not allowed."
                    }
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "l1QWxJ",
                  "type": "ref",
                  "ref": "ZbSPm",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "descendants": {
                    "At1fI": {
                      "content": "Q: Are there age restrictions?"
                    },
                    "lyRkf": {
                      "content": "A: Generally, participants must be at least 18 years old. Minors may participate with parental consent in some shorter events."
                    }
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
