                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Minsk Randonneurs is dedicated to the spirit of Audax Club Parisien. We emphasize self-reliance, camaraderie, and the pure joy of ultra-endurance cycling. What began with a handful of enthusiasts has grown into a nationwide movement, bringing the rich French tradition of long-distance cycling to the sprawling, beautiful roads of our homeland.",
